data.text:
Penguin Press, 2010. First edition. Hardcover. First printing, very good + hardcover shows just a hint of soil and shelf wear, else tight and clean, in very good + dust jacket (price at flap) that shows rubbing at edges and especially noticeable at rear panel. 904 pages with a set of black & white plates. Pleasing copy of this popular and highly regarded look at the first American president from the award winning author of Alexander Hamilton and The House of Morgan to name a couple. Very Good in Very Good DJ. Item #31258

ISBN: 1594202664
